{"lastModified":1775746334017,"uri":"c::9938368400::vessel::d5cca3d2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: \nSummer 2026: Italy - Sardinia\n\nThe luxurious charter yacht, Sunreef 60 Feel The Blue is a standout in the Sunreef Yachts Charter fleet, offering expansive indoor and outdoor spaces, innovative design, and unparalleled onboard comfort.\n\nDesigned in a modern nautical style with soft, soothing tones, Feel The Blue features five elegant en-suite cabins, comfortably accommodating up to 10 guests. The yacht’s vast saloon and spacious cockpit seamlessly merge into a semi-open lounging area, complemented by a stylish and functional galley.\n\nFor ultimate relaxation, guests can enjoy a spectacular front terrace and an impressive flybridge, complete with a jacuzzi, oversized sun pads, and a wet bar with a barbecue—perfect for soaking in breathtaking views.\n\nWith an array of top-tier amenities and a professional crew of three, Feel The Blue promises an unforgettable yachting experience, where comfort and style meet effortless luxury.","blueprint":{"name":"FEEL THE BLUE","images":["/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::d5cca3d2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::71d3a9a0-3a35-11f0-be95-497a75d27328/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::d5cca3d2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::71dc3520-3a35-11f0-be96-497a75d27328/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::d5cca3d2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::71dcaa50-3a35-11f0-be96-497a75d27328/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::d5cca3d2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::71d77a30-3a35-11f0-be95-497a75d27328/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::d5cca3d2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::71d53040-3a35-11f0-be95-497a75d27328/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::d5cca3d2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::71db23b0-3a35-11f0-be96-497a75d